title: The 411 on Covid Strains & Vaccines, with Dr Anna Blakney
description:
Dr. Anna Blakney joins Jillian to share all the current knowledge on the new strains of Covid-19, the differences between the various Covid vaccines, and everything in between that you need to know to protect yourself and your loved ones!
